13(a)(5) exempt fish farming activities, such as the maintenance of breeding
records, records of feed consumption related to fish production and the lik=
e,
would be considered as exempt activities under Sec 13(a)(5).</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph style=3D'margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in'>=
<span
style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>(d)<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>=
&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>A 20% tolerance for nonexemp=
t work
is permitted under both Secs 13(a)(5) and 13(b)(4). (See IB 784.116.)</span=
></p>

</div>

