<div class=3DWordSection6>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<h3>25f&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; HOMEWORKERS MAKING WREATHS - SEC
13(d), SECOND PART</h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<h4><b>25f00.&nbsp; General provisions and IB 780. Subpart K.</b></h4>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph style=3D'margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in'>=
<span
style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>(a)<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>=
&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>Sec 13(d), second part, exem=
pts
from the provisions of Secs 6, 7, and 12 “any homeworker engaged in the mak=
ing
of wreaths composed principally of natural holly, pine, cedar, or other
evergreens (including the harvesting of the evergreens or other forest prod=
ucts
used in making such wreaths)”.</span></p>

