<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<h4><b>25f01.&nbsp; “Wreaths”.</b></h4>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph style=3D'margin-left:.25in'><span style=3D'font=
-size:
11.0pt'>The term “wreaths”, as used in Sec 13(d), includes not only the typ=
ical
circular patterns but also other patterns, such as sprays and ropes.</span>=
</p>

