ons
and manner of operation clearly are entitled to exemption under Test B.</sp=
an></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraph style=3D'margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in'>=
<span
style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>(b)<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>=
&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style=3D'font-size:11.0pt'>Wage-Hour will consider the
exemption applicable in the year the new establishment begins operation if
